# Netlify redirects for SPA (Single Page Application)
# This ensures all routes are handled by index.html for client-side routing

# Force HTTPS - Redirect all HTTP traffic to HTTPS
http://sitecraftersz.co/*    https://www.sitecraftersz.co/:splat    301!
http://www.sitecraftersz.co/*    https://www.sitecraftersz.co/:splat    301!

# Force www - Redirect non-www to www
https://sitecraftersz.co/*    https://www.sitecraftersz.co/:splat    301!

# SPA routing - Redirect all routes to index.html with 200 status (must be last)
/*    /index.html   200
